<p>How to retrieve nested JSON to Objects in Java using <code>ObjectMapper</code>?</p>  <pre><code>{     "fullName": {         "firstName":"Ranjith",         "middleName":"Kumar",         "lastName":"xxxxx"     },     "phoneNo":"xxxxx",      "emailId":"xxxxx@gmail.com",      "passWd":"xxxxx" } </code></pre>  <p>Pojo:</p>  <pre><code>public class UserProfileModel {     private NameModel fullName = null;     private String phoneNo = null;     private String emailId = null;      private String passWd = null;     public String getuId() {         return uId;     }     .. } ... UserProfileModel userProfile =         objectMapper.readValue(userProfileJson.toString(),                                 UserProfileModel.class); .... </code></pre>